<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2325] investigate solr test failures using flex</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2325</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;We have a branch of Solr located here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/branches/solr&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucene/solr/branches/solr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently all the tests pass with lucene trunk jars.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I plopped in the flex jars and they do not, so I thought these might be interesting to look at.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
